<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss money</title><updated>2025-06-24T08:17:09.719264+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>2b448a1f3eb3ad98a36ebe8e966e5480</id><title>伊朗稱應特朗狗「乞求」而停火。。</title><updated>2025-06-24T14:43:12+08:00</updated><author><name>流西水股</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-24T14:43:12+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572970199"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572970199"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16323109" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572970199" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250624/20250624_e2f77f9d39564ff3de25HBfS4OrHdRNG.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d6cacc/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250624/20250624_e2f77f9d39564ff3de25HBfS4OrHdRNG.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16323109_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16323109&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1750747391314.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (246.86 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-6-24 14:43&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;伊朗國營電視台IRINN星期二（6月24日）清晨宣讀了停火聲明，宣稱德黑蘭對以色列「施加」停火，又讚揚了伊朗伊斯蘭革命衛隊的戰鬥。伊朗外交部長阿拉格奇（Abbas Araghchi）之前稱，若以色列停止攻擊，伊朗則無意繼續反擊。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;以色列則稱伊朗至少再策動了六次飛彈攻擊，紅大衛盾會（Magen David Adom）急救人員稱，至少四人死亡。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;星期一（23日）早些時候，伊朗對卡塔爾的美軍駐地實施報復性空襲，特朗普其後宣稱將分階段實施停火，伊朗會比以色列早12小時停止敵對行動。此言論引發外界混亂。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31964910&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1686976256685a5f05e3b7d6_17170843"/><published>2025-06-24T14:43:12+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>18cfc99ce2eeafd700f4bcb99c8a63cb</id><title>上面冇哂🐻，點升？</title><updated>2025-06-24T14:43:28+08:00</updated><author><name>忍不住想偷笑</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-24T14:43:28+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572970205"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572970205"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16323111" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572970205" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250624/20250624_af56d8f1e9813d0b1d50TjqvjLzzp7dn.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/053367/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250624/20250624_af56d8f1e9813d0b1d50TjqvjLzzp7dn.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16323111_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16323111&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_20250624_144143_Chrome.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (209.23 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-6-24 14:43&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt